quotes: Ah yes, checking boxes. Truly the mark of a champion... eventually.
Wow, you almost finished everything. Almost.
Every checkmark brings you closer to my respect. Almost.
Did you just skip that one? Bold strategy, cotton.
Mmm, love the smell of incomplete tasks in the morning.
You call that progress? My grandma clicks faster.
Look who's finally trying to be responsible.
A few more checks and you might even impress me. Might.
I'm not mad. Just… severely disappointed.
Don’t let that last unchecked box haunt you. Like it haunts me.
